                    <span>I love reading books that are funny and educational, it helps the information sink in. This is exactly that type of book, x3! Mr. Mathieu is truly a gifted writer and an enormously talented musician. Play on!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A MUST HAVE for anyone - musician or otherwise!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
